name: Hate4Hate
description:
In the world where we are hated. In the world where there is no peace. Where allies become enemies. Where pain is routine. And we are calloused with rage. Here, let's pay the same way. Hate for hate. We hate it, this is the environment, hostile, nothing for nothing, let's pay for everything with hate. this is the currency of exchange in the world of misery.

- LOYALTY

15-May-2019
São Paulo, SP.
